  <wpt lat="41.157309" lon="-96.042287">
    <time>2026-03-31T11:00:00</time>
    <name>GCBKX2A</name>
    <desc>Omaha Lunch #81 by LadyCache, Event Cache (1.0/1.0)</desc>
    <url>https://coord.info/GCBKX2A</url>
    <urlname>Omaha Lunch #81</urlname>
    <sym>Geocache</sym>
    <type>Geocache|Event Cache</type>
    <groundspeak:cache id="10340620" archived="False" available="True" xmlns:groundspeak="http://www.groundspeak.com/cache/1/0/1">
      <groundspeak:name>Omaha Lunch #81</groundspeak:name>
      <groundspeak:placed_by>LadyCache</groundspeak:placed_by>
      <groundspeak:owner id="568858">LadyCache</groundspeak:owner>
      <groundspeak:type>Event Cache</groundspeak:type>
      <groundspeak:container>Other</groundspeak:container>
      <groundspeak:attributes>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="24" inc="1">Wheelchair accessible</groundspeak:attribute>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="6" inc="1">Recommended for kids</groundspeak:attribute>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="25" inc="1">Parking nearby</groundspeak:attribute>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="28" inc="1">Public restrooms nearby</groundspeak:attribute>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="59" inc="1">Food nearby</groundspeak:attribute>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="27" inc="1">Drinking water nearby</groundspeak:attribute>
      </groundspeak:attributes>
      <groundspeak:difficulty>1.0</groundspeak:difficulty>
      <groundspeak:terrain>1.0</groundspeak:terrain>
      <groundspeak:country>United States</groundspeak:country>
      <groundspeak:state>Nebraska</groundspeak:state>
      <groundspeak:short_description html="True">&lt;b&gt;31 March 2026, 11:00 - 12:30&lt;/b&gt;</groundspeak:short_description>
      <groundspeak:long_description html="True">&lt;p&gt;Welcome to this monthly geocaching event series, which will hopefully take you to different locations each month for lunch in the greater Omaha area.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When:&lt;/strong&gt;  Tuesday, March 31 at 11:00 am - 12:30 pm &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Where:&lt;/strong&gt; Brownie&amp;#39;s Watering Hole   &lt;br /&gt;
125 E 2nd St&lt;br /&gt;
Papillion, NE 68046&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;As always, no purchase is necessary just come by to visit and have a good time. Please, no outside food or drink.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Event ownership is open to everyone, and the event owner decides on the date, time, and location, &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;preferably someplace new to the event&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; (see the long list of places already used below). If you would like to be the event owner for next month, please attend this current event or coordinate with the current event owner before the next event.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This monthly lunch has been going on since January 21, 2019!!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Past Omaha Lunch Events&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Omaha Lunch #001 at Don &amp;amp; Millies hosted by TeamDAAK&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #002 at The Corner Kick - Street Tacos and Sports Cantina hosted by jenny08_1015&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch Bunch #03 at A+ Buffet and Mongolian Grill hosted by BilltheBear&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch Bunch #04 at Pizza Ranch hosted by TnT Utter&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #005 at Farmhouse Cafe hosted by jenny08_1015&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #006 at Freddy&amp;#39;s Frozen Custard and Steakburgers hosted by TnT Utter&lt;br /&gt;
Lunch Bunch #007 at A+ Buffet and Mongolian Grill hosted hosted by BilltheBear&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #008 at Oakview Mall Food Court hosted by TeamDAAK&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #009 at 11-Worth Cafe hosted by jenny08_1015&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Breakfast (AKA Omaha Lunch) #10 at First Watch hosted by Monty12&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #11 at Pizza Ranch hosted by BilltheBear&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #12 at Dairy Queen by TeamDAAK&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #13 at Mar&amp;#39;s Bar and Grill by yhtak57&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #14 at Inner Rail Food Hall by Shadow Chasers&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #15 at Hy-Vee Food Court by Monty12&lt;br /&gt;
Island Lunch Event 19 (a.k.a. Omaha Lunch #16 ) at The Greek Islands by kilroy18&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #17 John&amp;#39;s Grecian Delight by Monty12&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #18 Halleck Park Duck Pond Island by kilroy18&lt;br /&gt;
